<subSubSection id="C316650AFFCBFFE3A7868FD8FE289E03" pageId="10" pageNumber="979" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BB33681FFCBFFE3A7868FD8FE289E03" blockId="10.[178,1085,1485,1565]" pageId="10" pageNumber="979">
N o t e. A turano mediterranean species known until 
<collectingCountry id="F31B7611FFCBFFE3A4358FD8FCA29DFD" box="[769,887,1485,1507]" name="Kazakhstan" pageId="10" pageNumber="979">Kazakhstan</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F31B7611FFCBFFE3A4818FD8FBCD9DFD" box="[949,1048,1485,1507]" name="Kyrgyzstan" pageId="10" pageNumber="979">Kirghizia</collectingCountry>
. In Western Europe, mainly on 
<taxonomicName id="4C0C4D02FFCBFFE3A6D28FFFFD8D9DE1" baseAuthorityName="LINNAVUORI" baseAuthorityYear="2007" box="[486,600,1514,1535]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="10" pageNumber="979" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Asteraceae</taxonomicName>
, also mentionned (but rarely) on 
<taxonomicName id="4C0C4D02FFCBFFE3A4FE8FFFFBEF9E1E" baseAuthorityName="PERICART" baseAuthorityYear="1998" box="[970,1082,1514,1536]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="979" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Lamiaceae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C0C4D02FFCBFFE3A7868C12FE2C9E03" authority="(PERICART 1998 b)" baseAuthorityName="PERICART" baseAuthorityYear="1998" box="[178,505,1542,1565]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="10" pageNumber="979" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">
Crassulaceae (
<bibRefCitation id="EF9D4B70FFCBFFE3A6708C1DFE279E03" author="PERICART J" box="[324,498,1542,1565]" pageId="10" pageNumber="979" pagination="84" refId="ref22046" refString="PERICART J. (1998 b): Hemipteres Lygaeidae euro-mediterraneens. In: Faune de France, t. 84 b. - Federation des Societes de sciences naturelles ed. Paris." type="book chapter" year="1998">PÉRİCART 1998b</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
